---
title: Double Turkey Curry and Crispy Chana Dal with Buttered Cilantro Rice
description: You'll be amazed at how much flavour is infused in this curry dish by marinating the turkey mixture with herbs and spices, then cooking it in creamy tikka sauce. To finish off this easy meal, everything gets spooned over buttery cilantro rice with a sprinkle of crispy chana dal for extra flavour and crunch!
